channel.title: Website Banner
channel.description:
Hey Guys
Ive recently started my own Topsite for several private servers games. At the moment I am having trouble designing something better than www.helbreath.biz
My site is www.hbtop100.net I was wondering if someone could make me a banner to the standard or better of www.helbreath.biz
Size? See the gradient box up the top thats empty :P? Well I hope you can make one to that size.
If your in it for the money than I can pay you $10 eGold. If your not and your just a kind soul ill try and make it up too you in another way.
Cheers GUYS!
P.S If it could say "Helbreath Top 100"
